      • getDisplayedSkinPartsMap

        @Nullable
public HashMap<WrappedPacketInSettings.DisplayedSkinPart,Boolean> getDisplayedSkinPartsMap()
        Get Displayed skin parts.

        It is possible for some keys to not exist. If that is the case, the server version is 1.7.10. 1.7.10 only sends the cape skin part.

        Returns:
        A map with a Skin Parts as a key, and a boolean as a value.

      • isDisplaySkinPartEnabled

        Is the skin part enabled.

        Returns:
